msgid "Chain"
msgstr "Katea"

msgid "Chains are metallic decoration blocks."
msgstr "Kateak burdinazko bloke apaingarriak dira."

msgid "Lantern"
msgstr "Farola"

msgid "Lanterns are light sources which can be placed on the top or the bottom of most blocks."
msgstr ""
"Farolak bloke gehienen goiko edo beheko aldean jar daitezkeen argi-iturriak "
"dira."

msgid "Soul Lantern"
msgstr "Arimen farola"
